    <itunes:summary>America's Test Kitchen is a real 2,500 square foot test kitchen located   just outside of Boston that is home to more than three-dozen full-time   cooks and product testers. Our mission is simple: to develop the   absolute best recipes for all of your favorite foods. To do this, we   test each recipe 30, 40, sometimes as many as 70 times, until we arrive   at the combination of ingredients, technique, temperature, cooking  time,  and equipment that yields the best, most-foolproof recipe.</itunes:summary>
